{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015960/extras/getToWorkText.png?t=1722812857\" /><br><br>The platformer where you're broke! <i>Slime Voyage</i> is a 2D-Platformer where you travel the world working odd jobs to get paid. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015960/extras/SlimeVoyageBreakdanceStaticChange.gif?t=1722812857\" /><br><br><i>So what's the plan...?</i> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015960/extras/getSlimey.png?t=1722812857\" /><br><br>You're a slime. Your goal? Some really, like <i><strong>REALLY</strong></i> cool sunglasses\u2122. <br>Work odd jobs to fund your dream and try not to destroy everything along the way. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015960/extras/gameplayTrim.gif?t=1722812857\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015960/extras/getToWorkStep.png?t=1722812857\" /><br><br>To fund his dreams, Slime takes up all kinds of job offers. <br>From <i>investigating the disappearance of a cult leader in a bottomless pit</i>, to a relaxing afternoon trimming the hedges of an overgrown flower garden...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015960/extras/gotAJob.gif?t=1722812857\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015960/extras/getPaid.png?t=1722812857\" /><br><br>Reap the sweet rewards!<br><br>Use your hard-earned money to splurge on house accessories, access secret worlds, and snatch those - really, like <strong><i>REALLY</i></strong> cool sunglasses\u2122.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/301596